		<div id="comment_body_65228199"><p>It used to be a large human cost of connecting consumer metrics to who to target in an advertising campaign.</p><p>AI LLM has swapped that cost with dumping a blender full of data metrics into a model and asking<br>- "Who is most likely to purchase a new dining table?"<br>- "What are the demographics of this household based on the furniture, floor space, city, postal code, sensor data and level of dirt?"</p><p>or<br>- "What political party does this household belong to based on the floor space and furniture?"</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_65228199">

</div>
</div>

